      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">💪</span>
          <span class="font-body text-on-surface"><span class="font-bold">Kekuatan Hebat:</span> 3–5× lebih kuat daripada kadbod gelombang standard</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">🪶</span>
          <span class="font-body text-on-surface"><span class="font-bold">Berat Ringan:</span> Honeycomb adalah 50–70% udara, mengurangkan kos penghantaran</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">🛡️</span>
          <span class="font-body text-on-surface"><span class="font-bold">Penyerapan Impak:</span> Struktur honeycomb mengalami lenturan dan menyerap kejutan tanpa memindahkan daya ke kandungan</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-primary font-bold">✓</span>
          <span class="font-body text-on-surface"><span class="font-bold">Konsisten:</span> Tiada titik lemah; kekuatan seragam di seluruh panel</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6">2. Panduan Ketebalan & Saiz Panel</h2>

      <table class="w-full text-sm mb-6">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-surface-variant/50 border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-3 px-3">Ketebalan</th>
            <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-3 px-3">Untuk Mesin</th>
            <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-3 px-3">Berat (kg)</th>
            <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-3 px-3">Harga/Panel</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">10–15mm</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">Mesin ringan (500–2,000 kg)</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">0.8–1.2</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">RM 4.00–6.00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">20–25mm</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">Mesin sederhana (2,000–5,000 kg)</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">1.5–2.0</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">RM 7.00–10.00</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">30–40mm</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">Mesin berat/sensitif (5,000+ kg)</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">2.5–3.5</td>
            <td class="py-3 px-3 text-on-surface">RM 10.00–15.00</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-6">3. Analisis ROI: Honeycomb vs. Kadbod Standard</h2>

      <div class="p-6 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg mb-6">
        <h4 class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Contoh: Melindungi Mesin CNC RM 150,000</h4>
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
              <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-2">Faktor Kos</th>
              <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-2">Kadbod Standard</th>
              <th class="text-left font-bold text-on-surface py-2">Honeycomb</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">Bahan pembungkus</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 800</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 1,200</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">Kos penghantaran</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 600 (berat)</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 250 (ringan)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-outline-variant/20">
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">Kebarangkalian kerosakan</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">8–12%</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">1–2%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">Kos pembaikan dijangkakan</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 12,000–18,000</td>
              <td class="py-2 text-on-surface">RM 1,500–3,000</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface text-sm mt-4">
          <span class="font-bold">Jumlah kos honeycomb:</span> RM 1,450 + RM 2,000 = RM 3,450<br>
          <span class="font-bold">Jumlah kos kadbod standard:</span> RM 1,400 + RM 15,000 = RM 16,400<br>
          <span class="font-bold">Jimat dengan honeycomb:</span> RM 12,950 setiap penghantaran
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12 p-8 bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg">
      <h3 class="font-headline text-lg font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Lindungi Mesin Anda dengan Panel Honeycomb</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Hubungi Quinocycle untuk sebut harga honeycomb tersuai. Daripada mesin kecil hingga peralatan besar, kami merancang penyelesaian perlindungan yang mencegah kerosakan dan mengurangkan kos keseluruhan penghantaran anda.
